channel.title: My computer
channel.description:
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,337280.0.html Referencing this^
I decided to put up a few pics of my new comp http://img249.imageshack.us/img249/2668/comp1000qb8.jpg
(specs on the bottom right)
FAQ:
"wtf monitor mounted on case?" no dumbass, it's mounted on the wall and the case is under it (saving space for me etc)
"wtf two temps" the green LED temp is the CPU temp, the blue one is the case temp (i have a temp probe that came with it)
"haha ur psu prolly sucks" i admit it should glow blue, but i bought the parts in USA so i don't care enough to send it back. OCZ makes good products.
"is that a webcam?" yes
"why so many buttons on keyboard?" macro's in WoW
"wireless g? get with the times" nou
"video card is huge, prolly sucks" not really
"what mobo is that?" EVGA x58, best choice there was due to the many overclocking capabilities
"i pooped my pants what do i do?" go clean yourself up in the washroom
